band-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/English-Teacher-band-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">英语老师</a>分享了他们充满活力的新单曲“Nearly Daffodils”——请在下面收听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">英语老师：来自英国吉他音乐中心的重要声音</a></strong></li></ul><p>利兹四人组的新曲目中，主唱莉莉·方丹 (Lily Fontaine) 将推动性的流行摇滚乐器与具有挑战性的自我实现相结合。</p><p> “《近乎水仙花》讲述的是心碎和接受未实现的潜力，”她在一份新闻声明中说。 “无论你多么想要某样东西，无论你为某样东西的成长或发展付出了多少努力，无论你能想象它的成果有多美丽；生活是个婊子，就像货运列车一样不可阻挡”。</p><p>听下面的新曲目。 </p><p><iframe title="英语老师 - 近乎水仙花（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x6xKTRZm3vI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>英语老师最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-recall-overcoming-imposter-syndrome-and-re-learning-how-to-be-a-performer-3498731">回忆了他们与冒名顶替综合症的斗争</a>，向<em>《NME》</em>透露，他们不断增长的信心如何让他们进入“一个新时代”。</p><p>该乐队成员还包括吉他手 Lewis Whiting、鼓手 Douglas Frost 和贝斯手 Nicholas Eden， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">他们作为最新的封面明星接受了 NME 采访</a>，并透露了他们最近几个月如何克服自我怀疑。</p><p>此次讨论还针对他们最近的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-english-teacher-reflective-new-single-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-radar-3481262">《世界上最大的铺路板》</a> ——这首歌曲最初制作于 2020 年，经过修改后将于今年夏天发行。</p><p> “这首歌对我们来说确实感觉像是一个新时代的开始，”怀廷说。 “有这么多人支持我们真是太棒了，但也很不和谐；这真是疯狂的两年。人们很容易忘记这一切发生得有多快。” </p><figure id="attachment_3495804" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3495804" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3495804" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700.jpg" alt="英语老师 (2023) 安迪·福特" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3495804" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：《NME》安迪·福特</figcaption></figure><p>在采访的其他地方，怀廷表示，一起创作新音乐的兴奋感“极大地”加强了乐队的联系。</p><p> “我觉得下一组歌曲将真正反映我们现在的处境，”他补充道。 “我们不想坐在一种声音中；一些听起来宏大的歌谣即将出现。我们有一点需要证明。”</p><p>英语老师将于本月晚些时候开始他们迄今为止最大的头条巡演。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/english-teacher-tickets/artist/5371524?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=zdmQRZTfwxyNUAZWPp1MB0h4UkFWG2zlnThV0M0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到所有演出日期并购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-english-teachers-dynamic-new-single-nearly-daffodils-3510922">听英语老师充满活力的新单曲“Nearly Daffodils”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《兄弟连》续集《空中大师》即将上映https://www.nme.com/news/tv/band-of-brothers-sequel-masters-of-the-air-release-date-3510911?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=band-of-brothers-sequel-空中大师发布日期Adam StarkeyFri, 06 Oct 2023 20:38:02 +0000 NewsTV NewsApple TV+ https://www.nme.com/?p=3510911 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="空中大师" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奥斯汀·巴特勒和巴里·基奥根主演这部战争剧</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/band-of-brothers-sequel-masters-of-the-air-release-date-3510911">《兄弟连》续集《空中大师》即将推出的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="空中大师" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《兄弟连》</em>和<em>《太平洋》</em>的后续系列<em>《空中大师》</em>已经收到了发行日期和首发图片 - 请在下面查看。</p><p>这部即将上映的战争剧的前两集将于明年 1 月 26 日星期五在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>上在全球首播，后续七集将在 2024 年 3 月 15 日之前每周播出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/austin-butler-elvis-interview-3250990">奥斯汀·巴特勒谈扮演埃尔维斯·普雷斯利：“我如何让我的灵魂遇见他的灵魂？”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该剧由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steven-spielberg">史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hanks">汤姆·汉克斯</a>和加里·戈兹曼重聚，他们共同制作了<em>《兄弟连》</em>和 2010 年的<em>《太平洋》</em> 。该剧由约翰·奥尔洛夫编剧，导演包括卡里·福永（《<em>无暇赴死</em>》）、安娜·博登和瑞安·弗莱克（《<em>半个尼尔森</em>》）、迪·里斯（《<em>泥土之界</em>》）和蒂姆·范·帕滕（ <em>《黑镜》</em> ）。</p><p> <em>《空中大师》</em>讲述了二战期间美国第 100 轰炸大队对纳粹德国进行轰炸袭击的真实故事。该剧改编自唐纳德·L·米勒的同名小说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510913" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510913" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3510913 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2.jpg" alt="空中大师" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510913" class="wp-caption-text">安东尼·博伊尔在《空中大师》中。图片来源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p>如第一张图片所示，该剧主演包括奥斯汀·巴特勒（ <em>《猫王》</em> ）、卡勒姆·特纳（ <em>《神奇动物</em>》）、安东尼·博伊尔（ <em>《俄罗斯方块》）、内特·曼、拉弗蒂·洛、巴里·基奥根（《伊尼舍林女妖</em><em>》</em> ）、乔赛亚·克罗斯、布兰登·库克和Ncuti Gatwa（<em>性教育</em>）。</p><p>谈到该剧，戈兹曼表示：“ <em>《空中大师》</em>是向第八空军的勇敢战士们致敬，他们通过勇气和兄弟情谊帮助在第二次世界大战中击败了纳粹德国。</p><p> “汤姆和史蒂文一直想以电影的方式呈现我们的作者唐·米勒所说的这一‘战争史上的奇特事件’。我们很高兴 Apple TV+ 为我们提供了机会，将银幕上和镜头后众多才华横溢的人们的努力结合起来，来讲述这个重要的故事。”</p><p> <em>《兄弟连》</em>于 2001 年上映，讲述了第 506 伞兵步兵团的一个营的故事，受到了广泛好评。与此同时，其姊妹剧<em>《太平洋》</em>讲述了海军陆战队第一师的三名海军陆战队员在该地区作战的经历。</p><p>您可以在下面查看<em>空中大师</em>的更多图片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510916" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510916" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510916" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air.jpg" alt="空中大师" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Barry-Keoghan-Masters-Of-The-Air-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510916" class="wp-caption-text">巴里·基奥根在《空中大师》中。图片来源：苹果</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3510918" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510918" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510918" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-4.jpg" alt="空中大师" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Masters-Of-The-Air-4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/u